### Vendored monorepo build artifacts (crates/ + packages/) ###
# Rust build artifacts
target/

# packages/ Bun workspace (workspace root, node-modules layout).
# Scoped to packages/ so the rest of the dotfiles repo is unaffected. The
# single workspace-root packages/bun.lock is intentionally TRACKED (lockfile
# convention, like the Rust Cargo.lock); per-member dist/ build output is not.
packages/node_modules/
packages/*/node_modules/
packages/*/dist/
.turbo/
packages/.turbo/
packages/*/.turbo/

