### Secrets cache — only the GPG-encrypted .asc is committable ###
# chezmoi-secrets-sync builds the bundle in memory and only ever writes .json.asc,
# but this guard makes a stray plaintext (or .tmp) variant impossible to commit.
.chezmoitemplates/secrets-bundle.json*
!.chezmoitemplates/secrets-bundle.json.asc
